					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/30/who-is-jamie-dimon/">&#8220;Who is Jamie&nbsp;Dimon?&#8221;</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">July 30, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/30/who-is-jamie-dimon/#comments" title="Comment on &#8220;Who is Jamie&nbsp;Dimon?&#8221;">1 Comment</a></span>
