			<div class="post-4894 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-jp-morgan">

				<div class="entry">

					<h2><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/13/web-extra-chris-whalen-is-jp-morgan-blowing-hot-air-with-clawbacks-plus-natural-gas-forecasts/">Web Extra Chris Whalen: Is JP Morgan blowing hot air with clawbacks? Plus, Natural Gas&nbsp;forecasts</a></h2>

					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">July 13, 2012</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2012/07/13/web-extra-chris-whalen-is-jp-morgan-blowing-hot-air-with-clawbacks-plus-natural-gas-forecasts/#respond" title="Comment on Web Extra Chris Whalen: Is JP Morgan blowing hot air with clawbacks? Plus, Natural Gas&nbsp;forecasts">Leave a comment</a></span>
																				</p>
					</div>

					<span class='embed-youtube' style='text-align:center; display: block;'><iframe class='youtube-player' type='text/html' width='630' height='385' src='http://www.youtube.com/embed/jRCJTbSA4io?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;fs=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;wmode=transparent' frameborder='0'></iframe></span>
<div class="clear"></div>

				</div>

				<div class="post-meta">
					<p>
						<span class="categories">Filed under <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/category/jp-morgan/" rel="category tag">JP Morgan</a></span>
